(1, 1, 'Un commentateur WordPress', 'wapuu@wordpress.example', 'https://wordpress.org/', '', '2020-12-14 10:01:48', '2020-12-14 09:01:48', 'Bonjour, ceci est un commentaire.\nPour débuter avec la modération, la modification et la suppression de commentaires, veuillez visiter l’écran des Commentaires dans le Tableau de bord.\nLes avatars des personnes qui commentent arrivent depuis <a href=\"https://gravatar.com\">Gravatar</a>.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', 'comment', 0, 0),
(2, 84, 'Greg', 'greg.beaucaire@gmail.com', 'http://localhost', '::1', '2020-12-14 14:58:28', '2020-12-14 13:58:28', 'Ceci est un commentaire test : The simple things in life I know I listed more than 6 things there\'s no such thing as a typical Friday night I\'m a big fan of. Nothing too complicated if you think we have something in common joking around new friends Werner Herzog, amazing women I\'ve met discussing politics bored at home I\'m really good at someone who shares my sense of humor. Recently moved back crossfit Sunday funday short-term dating training for the marathon recently moved back.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:83.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/83.0', 'comment', 0, 1);
